title: House of Reps top-shot, Wale Osinubi weds again
text:
Home » Entertainment » House of Reps top-shot, Wale Osinubi weds again House of Reps top-shot, Wale Osinubi weds again On 12:18 am In Entertainment by Nwafor Polycarp Comments 
The city of Ijebu Ode, Ogun State stood still on Sunday, January 29, 2017 as it witnessed the glamorous wedding between House of Representatives member, Otunba Adewale Osinubi and pretty FCMB big babe, Mariam Oluwatobi Mebude. 
The groom, who is also the CEO of Wesco Lotto & Lottery tied the nuptial knot with his long-time fiancee, who hails from the popular Mebude Dynasty in Ijebu Ode and a top staff of the Otunba Subomi Balogun owned First City Monument Bank in an ‘all in one” ceremony, that had all the movers and shakers of Ogun State social circle in attendance. •Otunba and chief Mrs Adewale Osinubi 
Notable faces at the lavish wedding ceremony, which was held at the famous Adeola Odutola hall, include, former Ogun State Governor, Otunba Gbenga Daniel, Senator Buruji Kashamu, Senator Lekan Mustapha, UPN Governorship Candidate in the 2015 elections, Prince Rotimi Paseda, and his PDP counterpart, Prince Gboyega Nasir Isiaka, while entertainment was provided by Multiple awards winning Fuji act, Kolade Onanuga. Nwafor Polycarp
